{"id":69,"date":"2019-12-23T15:12:02","date_gmt":"2019-12-23T15:12:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.incoproip.com\/?post_type=industry&#038;p=69"},"modified":"2021-05-06T16:27:45","modified_gmt":"2021-05-06T16:27:45","slug":"luxury-fashion","status":"publish","type":"industry","link":"https:\/\/www.incoproip.com\/industries\/luxury-fashion\/","title":{"rendered":"Luxury &#038; Fashion"},"content":{"rendered":"<section class=\"industry-jumbotron\">\n    <div class=\"jumbotron__img\">\n        <img\n            srcset=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Catwalking-through-europe_hero-banner1920x620-576x0-c-default.jpg\"\n            src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Catwalking-through-europe_hero-banner1920x620-48x0-c-default.jpg\"\n            data-sizes=\"auto\"\n            data-srcset=\"\n              \/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Catwalking-through-europe_hero-banner1920x620-576x0-c-default.jpg 576w,\n              \/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Catwalking-through-europe_hero-banner1920x620-992x0-c-default.jpg 992w,\n              \/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Catwalking-through-europe_hero-banner1920x620-1200x0-c-default.jpg 1200w,\n              \/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Catwalking-through-europe_hero-banner1920x620-1920x0-c-default.jpg 1920w\"\n            data-src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/Catwalking-through-europe_hero-banner1920x620-1920x0-c-default.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Catwalking&#x20;through&#x20;Europe,&#x20;from&#x20;Incopro&#x27;s&#x20;blog\"\n            class=\"lazyload blur-up\" \/>\n        <div class=\"jumbotron__overlay\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>The online counterfeit luxury <br \/>\r\nmarket is estimated at<span>$30.3 billion <\/span><\/h2>\n        <p>This is a concerning figure that is likely to grow as consumers unknowingly purchasing fake products on social media platforms and online ecommerce marketplaces. The threat is particularly severe for the fashion industry as it is consistently the single-largest target for counterfeiting activity in regions such as the US.<br \/>\r\n<br \/>\r\nWhen consumers purchase counterfeit luxury and fashion goods, they often think of it as being a victimless purchase. However, beyond the wider social and human rights issues that come with the production of these illegitimate goods, there are also health risks from the unsafe materials that are used. <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<section class=\"industry-statistics\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading-branded\">Did you know?<\/h2>\n        <div class=\"statistics\">\n                        <div class=\"statistic\">\n                                <h4 class=\"statistic__figure brand--primary\">52%<\/h4>\n                <p>of US respondents said they lost trust in a brand after unintentionally purchasing a product they believed was genuine.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"statistic\">\n                                <h4 class=\"statistic__figure brand--primary\">32% <\/h4>\n                <p>of US respondents said they would buy fake clothing.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"statistic\">\n                                <h4 class=\"statistic__figure brand--primary\">3.3%<\/h4>\n                <p>of all global trade is suspected to be counterfeit.<\/p>\n                            <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n        <div class=\"approach\">\n            <div class=\"approach__inner\">\n                <div>\n                    <h3>HOW CAN INCOPRO HELP?<\/h3>\n                    <p>Incopro works with some of the largest and best-known fashion brands in the world, preventing counterfeit luxury goods from reaching their consumers. Our technology, Talisman, scrapes the internet to identify the biggest threats to your brand and provide the mechanism to have these enforced and removed.<br \/>\r\n<br \/>\r\nTo learn about our approach in detail, follow the link here.<\/p>\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.incoproip.com\/difference\/approach\/\" title=\"HOW&#x20;CAN&#x20;INCOPRO&#x20;HELP&#x3F;\"  class=\"btn btn--primary\">Our Approach<\/a>\n                <\/div>\n                <div>\n                    <div class=\"approach__img-wrap\">\n                        <img\n                            src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/incopro-case-study-luxury-industry-48x0-c-default.jpg\"\n                            data-src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/incopro-case-study-luxury-industry-840x0-c-default.jpg\"\n                            alt=\"The&#x20;quantitative&#x20;impact&#x20;of&#x20;an&#x20;effective&#x20;brand&#x20;protection&#x20;strategy,&#x20;an&#x20;Incopro&#x20;case&#x20;study\"\n                            class=\"approach__img lazyload blur-up\" \/>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<section class=\"featured-case-study\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n                <h2 class=\"heading-branded\">Featured case study<\/h2>\n                <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"featured-case-study__thumbnail\">\n                                <div class=\"featured-case-study__thumbnail-wrapper\">\n                    <img\n                        src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Ted-Baker-case-study-banner-V2-12x0-c-default.jpg\"\n                        data-src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/Ted-Baker-case-study-banner-V2-860x0-c-default.jpg\"\n                        alt=\"Case&#x20;Study&#x20;&#x7C;&#x20;Ted&#x20;Baker&amp;&#x23;8217&#x3B;s&#x20;intelligence-led&#x20;approach&#x20;to&#x20;brand&#x20;protection\"\n                        class=\"lazyload blur-up\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"featured-case-study__testimonial\">\n                <div class=\"featured-case-study